Flag bap_std
  Description: Build BAP Standard Library
  Default: false

Library bap
  Path:            lib/bap
  Build$:          flag(everything) || flag(bap_std)
  FindLibName:     bap
  CompiledObject:  best
  BuildDepends:    bap.disasm,
                   bap.image,
                   bap.sema,
                   bap.types,
                   bap-bundle,
                   bap-main,
                   bap-future,
